WITH o, p, q, r, s, t

MATCH (o)-[:RELATIONSHIP]->(q)
MATCH (o)-[:RELATIONSHIP]->(r)

MATCH (q)<-[:RELATIONSHIP]-(o)

MATCH (o)-[rel:COMMENT]->(r)
MATCH (s)-[rel:COMMENT]->(r)
MATCH (t)-[rel:COMMENT]->(r)
